{
  "page": "Passages of the Dead",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><i><b>Passages of the Dead</b></i> is a work by Maester <a href=\"/index.php/Kennet_(maester)\" title=\"Kennet (maester)\">Kennet</a> about the <a href=\"/index.php/Barrow\" title=\"Barrow\">barrow</a> fields, graves, and tombs of the <a href=\"/index.php/North\" title=\"North\">north</a>. It has information about the burials of <a href=\"/index.php/Giants\" title=\"Giants\">giants</a> and mentions a legendary curse on the <a href=\"/index.php/Great_Barrow\" title=\"Great Barrow\">Great Barrow</a>. Kennet wrote his study while serving Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Cregan_Stark\" title=\"Cregan Stark\">Cregan Stark</a> at <a href=\"/index.php/Winterfell\" title=\"Winterfell\">Winterfell</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_dawn_age.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_dawn_age.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Passages_of_the_Dead&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_dawn_age.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_dawn_age.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i>, The Dawn Age.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260403153503\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.